$\mu = \sum m_\ell$ (companion-note scale) & $1.88303$ & $0.6674136$ & $7.47 \times 10^{-4}$ \\
$\mu = 2$~GeV (conventional reference) & $2.00000$ & $0.6681029$ & $1.44 \times 10^{-3}$ \\
$\mu = 1.5$~GeV (intermediate) & $1.50000$ & $0.6644741$ & $2.19 \times 10^{-3}$ \\
